{"tid":977651,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"我相信高普永遠會記得今年2月24日 記得自己當日一時之氣 害左利物浦全季","createTime":"2019-01-11T10:34:48.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-11T11:04:59.000Z","uid":92376,"like":6,"dislike":10,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"bd38fd3710b152747b47add209eaf2e8d30cbd4b","tid":977651,"uid":92376,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-11T10:34:48.000Z","msg":"因為傷兵滿營既關係+連懦夫都收山中<br />\n所以黎緊利記將會開始失分<br />\n去到2月24日第27輪聯賽前預料只係領先曼城3分同熱狗4分 再失分就會比曼城追過<br />\n而24號當日既比賽去到補時<br />\n可憐既高普望住場上既積分牌<br />\n先至識得後悔<br />\n去年有一個叫摩連奴既大好人比佢玩死左<br />\n剃人頭者 人亦剃其頭<br />\n劇本一早寫定左<br />\n從此曼城穩佔榜首 直到季尾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n高普悔不當初 只好黯然下台<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0fdbcd1fa64f9c68a3c94d7ca1c49344a9cd825e","tid":977651,"uid":5191,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-11T10:46:54.000Z","msg":"哭了"},{"pid":"ecca711a85122d56eac47de778c72ba561eeb466","tid":977651,"uid":200801,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-11T11:04:59.000Z","msg":"諗多咗喇，獌狗踢多幾場就見底啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}